>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T08:20:03.000Z","msg":"反上腦 呢d錢唔充公 <br />\n等佢坐完出黎再住山頂咩<br />\n<br />\n定係話賣淫阿頭都好黃 話晒黃色事業<br />\n手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc52dc3539cd675f52cce435471e4a65f12f13b7","tid":2397180,"uid":73276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T08:25:59.000Z","msg":"係咩網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cddc5021988483a534139fbd250a6d3a3d567c27","tid":2397180,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f0765246fe27aaf8d8f419080d2989ca4f7a44b","tid":2397180,"uid":91771,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T08:17:00.000Z","msg":"賠3千萬坐3船年<br />\n唔賠坐10年<br />\n點揀好呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T10:19:48.000Z","msg":"呢啲仆街賠3000萬之後10年就賺3億啦"},{"pid":"c4a63ebca8a80ee364b18e7015d0aef97111fada","tid":2397180,"uid":154255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53d6f87722c72038d057d6fdbbc56e1ff3d96c4c","tid":2397180,"uid":50101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T08:17:34.000Z","msg":"坐十年就有3300萬，連登仔肯定爭崩頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T10:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁少，仲要黃金十年<br />\n冇10憶都唔坐啦"}]}